data.name: Adult Cruiser 26" + Ally Cat
data.description:
The Ally Cat allows your child to learn how to ride while staying safely behind you during your ride.  Rental includes the 26″ adult cruiser.

Recommended for children 4 to 10 years old and up to 85 pounds with a recommended 2-1 adult weight-to-child weight ratio.
